                                                <h3 class="gdlr-core-title-item-title gdlr-core-skin-title " style="font-size: 24px ;font-weight: 700 ;letter-spacing: 0px ;text-transform: none ;color: #293a5b ;">Entebbe International Airport Set to Open on October 1, 2020</h3></div>
